(author: ethercat_mill)
(version: 1.0)
(Set active WCO Z to the given coordinate at the current position)
(Use after probing or touching off: e.g. 0.05 for a 50um shim, -5 for 5mm below the part)

o<set_wco_z> sub
  #<z_value> = #1

  (Cancel G92 offsets)
  G92.1

  (Set current position to Z = #<z_value> in active WCO)
  G10 L20 P0 Z#<z_value>

o<set_wco_z> endsub [1]

M2
